22
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:24,840
Kenapa kau gadaikan begitu saja?

23
00:02:26,410 --> 00:02:28,910
Jika mau pelat Maharani,
kau bisa minta langsung padaku.

24
00:02:29,740 --> 00:02:31,520
