tak mencintaiku.

491
00:36:11,330 --> 00:36:12,320
Ada urusan apa?

492
00:36:12,620 --> 00:36:13,520
Cepat.

493
00:36:13,620 --> 00:36:14,630
Jangan terlalu dekat.

494
00:36:14,630 --> 00:36:15,760
Aku ingin bicara denganmu.

495
00:36:15,980 --> 00:36:18,390
