Sudah selesai?

526
00:38:27,090 --> 00:38:28,430
Pergilah jika sudah selesai.

527
00:38:29,420 --> 00:38:30,950
Lain kali, takkan kuberi tahu kau.

528
00:38:32,660 --> 00:38:34,320
Dasar Mo Liancheng.

529
00:38:41,330 --> 00:38:42,840
Dasar Mo Liancheng sial.

